_sText:
This is version -1 of the bridge shown here : http://www.fpsbanana.com/prefabs/2158 .
It is version -1, because I got rid of the roof, so now it is alot more basic looking, but people wanted me to upload it without the roof, and here it is!
And to everyone that gave me feedback on the two others, thanks alot for taking the time :D, it helped me update and realise what was wrong, good community *Pats community's head*.
Anyways, yeah the file up for download includes the .vmf of the prefab for use in hammer, and a .bsp to test out the bridge ingame, readily compiled, just pop it in your maps folder and check it out!
